                  <h3>Team 1</h3>
                  <p>길영재 박유선 양진 정하빈</p>
              </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 hero-feature">
        <a href="/team2">
          <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="<%=image_path("team2/thumbnail_team2.jpg")%>" alt="">
              <div class="caption">
                  <h3>Team 2</h3>
                  <p>서용혁 최소원 김희재</p>
              </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 hero-feature">
        <a href="/team3">
          <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="<%=image_path("team3/thumbnail_team3.jpg")%>" alt="">
              <div class="caption">
                  <h3>Team 3</h3>
                  <p>김태수 김태진 김택수 전대성</p>
              </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 hero-feature">
        <a href="/team4">
          <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="<%=image_path("team4/thumbnail_team4.jpg")%>" alt="">
              <div class="caption">
                  <h3>Team 4</h3>
                  <p>김지완 빈경민 이지영 윤동하</p>
              </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <hr>
    <br>
    
    <div>
      <img src="<%=image_path("festival_main.jpg")%>" style="width:100%;">
    </div>
  </div> <!-- container end -->
  
  <footer style="height:80px; text-align:center; background:beige; margin-top:50px;">
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
              <p style="margin-top:30px;">Copyright &copy; 멋쟁이 사자처럼xUNIST</p>
          </div>
      </div>
  </footer>
